{"tid":1684023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為721，831，陳彥霖同學等案件各自成立調查及關注組","createTime":"2019-10-31T02:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T03:24:51.000Z","uid":201178,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ff1c09e55fb77b1549a530aaabac389bc2ecf38f","tid":1684023,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:01:09.000Z","msg":"如果要你數，一路以黎有幾多野你唔記得左？<br />\n612,721,831 <br />\n緊急法面具法<br />\n百幾個冇可疑自殺案<br />\n家人被消失案 <br />\n屯門大型可疑氣體<br />\n等等等等 <br />\n你有幾多野唔記得左？又有幾多野冇人keep track住？ <br />\n政府無能，佢哋做唔到既野就我做。<br />\n<br />\n我會為每一件，每一位可疑死亡事件成立追查小組，確保每一件，係每一件事，政府都要作出正面回應。你哋殺左人，唔可以就咁算。<br />\n我哋好善忘，但我唔會忘記你點樣殘害我哋香港人。<br />\n各大平台組織中，有意見歡迎留低。<br />\n<br />\n最後：本人絕不自殺。全家黃到發光。唔出聲就係比人控制左。"},{"pid":"5e40561ba348b359b02c54493e78aabe659bddae","tid":1684023,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:08:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8c5aaf442737f811b8f80a7cc4fcf593291306c","tid":1684023,"uid":138594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:12:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fc8042965908c04e97fabc92f5dc1d72106f8c6","tid":1684023,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:17:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7eca1a6e884cf78efa27583fc57a154fd1816f63","tid":1684023,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:27:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7796bca62cc9ce1537b22a12f757233a940126a0","tid":1684023,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1c1243e689b9ea6bad70896f803f1e3c34309c","tid":1684023,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T05:47:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1772af43fd8426ff57bc3e880c7cc626c500960e","tid":1684023,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T06:06:53.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">陳彥霖</span><br />\n一個想自己第時小朋友有未來的小女孩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jp2nEp2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjp2nEp2.jpg&h=04c8d37a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ch.yinlam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fch.yinlam&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=d7ffaaf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ch.yinlam</a><br />\n===========================<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔可以俾陳彥霖事件不了了之<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[重要發現] 陳彥霖事件討論分析(多圖)<br />\n</span><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679271</a>"},{"pid":"86bec1f2ca8c4a9d75b1309e8cf8e930cfb366ce","tid":1684023,"uid":233316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a8dc78e443b8dbd685a2ae2e1abeb4279d6567","tid":1684023,"uid":252064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:28:04.000Z","msg":"辛苦您啦<br />\n每人做啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CskEniY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCskEniY.jpg&h=e400e0c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adb3c734affff0b501ac908ffcb5c25ab35ac8a6","tid":1684023,"uid":30115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:36:09.000Z","msg":"不能麻木"},{"pid":"1bf827fa424886516f535141289891d967520937","tid":1684